            "LongDescWithoutEidolon": "<span>Deals Ice DMG equal to </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>300%</span></span><span> of Jingliu's ATK to a single enemy, and deals Ice DMG equal to </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>150%</span></span><span> of Jingliu's ATK to any adjacent enemies. Gains <span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>1</span> stack(s) of Syzygy after attack ends.</span>",
            "LongDescWithEidolon": "<span>Deals Ice DMG equal to </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>324%</span></span><span> of Jingliu's ATK to a single enemy, and deals Ice DMG equal to </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>162%</span></span><span> of Jingliu's ATK to any adjacent enemies. Gains <span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>1</span> stack(s) of Syzygy after attack ends.</span>"
