            "Type": "Talent",
            "LongDescWithoutEidolon": "<span>After each hit dealt during an attack, Dan Heng • Imbibitor Lunae gains 1 stack of Righteous Heart, increasing his DMG by </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>10%</span></span><span>. This effect can stack up to <span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>6</span> time(s), lasting until the end of his turn.</span>",
            "LongDescWithEidolon": "<span>After each hit dealt during an attack, Dan Heng • Imbibitor Lunae gains 1 stack of Righteous Heart, increasing his DMG by </span><span style='color:#f29e38ff'><span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>11%</span></span><span>. This effect can stack up to <span style='whiteSpace: \"nowrap\"'>6</span> time(s), lasting until the end of his turn.</span>"
